    "DisplayTitle": "Apprehend Bounty: [TargetName] (HRT)",
    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nmicroTech Protection Services is looking for a qualified bounty hunter to apprehend ~mission(TargetName) who has so far been able to evade capture. They are coordinating an active raid at ~mission(Location|Address), and we believe that they may finally be lured out of hiding if their forces there attacking the ~mission(Location) are faced with strong enough resistance. \n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation to ~mission(Location|Address).\n\u2022 Neutralize ~mission(TargetName)\u2019s criminal associates near the ~mission(Location) to draw the target into the open.\n\u2022 Neutralize ~mission(TargetName); using force if necessary.\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Access to combat equipment and mode of transport.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Ability to handle high pressure situations.",
